'''Mauritania''' ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. ''Mauritania'' e leboa bodikela la Afrika, e wela seleteng sa [[Afrika Bodikela]].

''Mauritania'' e agišane le : 
* [[Senegal]] (borwa bodikela),
* [[Mali]] (bohlabela le borwa bohlabela),
* [[Algeria]] (leboa bohlabela),
* [[Western Sahara]] (leboa bodikela), bogolo bja naga e le [[Morocco]].

